{
  "stem": "17044.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 244.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then one day, my sister was-- she escaped to [NON-ENGLISH] to study.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Came on back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Instead to retreat with Russians, she came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She wanted to be with the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were happy to see her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one of-- the opposite one, and my older brother for me, he retreat to Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we figured he'll survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were crying of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But then we saw what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were happy what he escaped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He'll maybe the only one to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chaim.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a while, we find out that he died from hunger, from sickness, and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister, which she did a stupid thing, instead to escape with the friends, but they survived. they retreat to Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she came back and she-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah, she saw my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Couple days after she came back, a truck appeared in the front of my house, when I used to live there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they round up people-- only men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A couple hours before this, my father told me to take the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] Sefer Torah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is a big story of this, like I told you before, that my grandmother was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] commit herself to fast.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The same thing-- my father promised if he live, the first child will live, he will write a Sefer Torah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he wrote a Sefer Torah for three years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For three years, he kept the people to write the story, make the skin, and everything, feed them and pay them for three years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was a big Sefer Torah in honor of my father, given to the shul.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we wouldn't go already pray in shul, by then Germans-- we couldn't go because we was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They wouldn't let us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
